===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}
# (c. 396–314 {{B.C.E.}}) An Ancient Greek [[philosopher]], mathematician, and the second leader (scholarch) of the [[Plato|Platonic]] [[Academy]] from 339 to 314 {{B.C.E.}}.
